definitions.definition: Of, relating to, or belonging to a city , a citizen, or citizenship; municipal or civil.
examples: Thousands of people came to the Civic Center to show off their civic pride.

definitions.definition: Of or relating to the citizen, or of good citizenship and its rights and duties.
